## 3. معمارية خط التجميع الدفاعي (Pipeline)

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                        HTTP Request                             │
└──────────────────────────┬──────────────────────────────────────┘
                           ▼
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  [0] WAFSettings Check ──── master on/off switch                │
│  [1] Honeypot Check ─────── 75 decoy paths, instant blacklist   │
│  [1.1] Adaptive Rate Limiter ─ Token Bucket per IP/User         │
│  [1.2] ATO Protector ────── Credential Stuffing detection       │
│  [1.3] Client Fingerprinting ─ JA3 + Header order              │
│  [1.4] API Schema Validation ─ OpenAPI contract enforcement     │
│  [2]  WAF Preprocessor ──── 9 decode steps, up to 6 iterations  │
│  [2.5] Shadow Autopilot ─── passive traffic observation         │
│  [3]  Feature Extractor ─── 10 numerical features from payload  │
│                                                                 │
│  [4]  AI Models Layer                                           │
│         ├── [4a] NLP Model  (1D-CNN+BiLSTM)  → nlp_score       │
│         ├── [4b] Bot Detector (XGBoost)       → bot_score       │
│         ├── [4c] Threat Intel (AbuseIPDB/OTX) → reputation      │
│         └── [4d] Heuristic Anomaly           → anomaly_score    │
│                                                                 │
│  [5]  Risk Scoring Engine ─ Weighted sum → [0.0, 1.0]          │
│  [6]  Policy Decision ───── ALLOW / CHALLENGE / SOFT_BLOCK / BLOCK │
│  [7]  Self-Learning Logger ─ write to waf_training_data (DB)    │
│  [8]  GNN Session Logger ── append to session_logs.csv          │
│  [9]  Live Broadcast ────── WebSocket → SOC Dashboard           │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

